Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.06,0:01:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉与桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第48话 想回到相遇的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何你目不转睛的盯着我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是防止化脓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是止痛的涂抹药
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  纱布与绷带我带了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  那么我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是送药过来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  至少和犬夜叉握手言和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再为了小事就吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和犬夜叉吵过架
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在怎么想都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但怎能将你交给奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能从奈落手里保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我而已不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵架的事我居然完全忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇无精打采的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…这也不是没有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个光是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  戈薇姑娘又回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你和桔梗见面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且让戈薇姑娘看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…被看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你还厚着脸皮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你满面佛光喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  那种大彻大悟的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉目不转睛的盯着我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉似乎打算说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因为我害怕听见而逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉一定下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉与桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因奈落的陷阱而彼此憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗亦追随犬夜叉而死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且拆散两人的奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再度袭击桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在怎么想都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但怎能将你交给奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能保护你的只有我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就没有我介入的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我还是放不下桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  我已经不会再见你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能再见你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗为了犬夜叉\N连命都豁出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本比不上她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也无法回到犬夜叉那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉也不会来接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把四魂碎片带来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是还给他比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错…把这个还回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后一切都会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我则回到普通的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么早就回来不说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从回来之后又都不说话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐是怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大拇指?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和犬夜叉哥哥吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈…\N爸爸  方便的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这份荷包蛋给你吃好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些腌罗卜很有口感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道很不错喔  吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  碗不用洗没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待会我会一起洗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈…\N姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要做什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道妈妈都不担心姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:09:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个腌罗卜真的很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出院了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是身体\N出现了不明的斑点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装病的理由跟点子用光了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂且不管这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再装傻啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是和先前明明脚踏两条船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又爱吃醋的\N粗暴任性男人的关系呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实的分手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们好像说了什么不该说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.39,0:09:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎狠狠的被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是戈薇甩掉他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还喜欢着那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过呢  已经完全没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经不在意了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  所以就什么都别再问了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是再碰触伤口的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种假笑好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇跟钢牙要好一点就发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己却一心一意的跟桔梗跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就为了这么轻率的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  去见戈薇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗唆耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经决定再也不去见她了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有搞错啊  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要你取回被戈薇姑娘\N带回去的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你能通过那口井吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:11:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只为了四魂碎片?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是戈薇怎么样无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉已经选择了桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要戈薇姑娘回来才是残酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉啊  这样真的妥当吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啦  枫姥姥连你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的桔梗姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是由骨灰与土所创造的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就是不属于\N这个世界的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样  魂魄还是桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不明白吗  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追根究底\N你们在这世上是无法结合的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗姐姐想要的\N只是和你共赴黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓  就如桔梗所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和她一同下地狱去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那是我与桔梗的命运…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片得拿去还他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果归还这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就再也见不到犬夜叉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跟随桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想听那些话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有桔梗的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…是这么坏的女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在的表情一定很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的表情不能和犬夜叉相见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎片…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了…这棵树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是  将犬夜叉封印的树吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五百年前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里  第一次遇见犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那什么呆滞的表情啊  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经老的痴呆了吗  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一箭解决它啊  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像上次解决我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗桔梗的  到底在叫谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听好了\N我的名字叫做…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我要和他相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道这么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如当初不要相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想见他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想再一次见到犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然喜欢上犬夜叉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何时  变得这么喜欢他了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你待在神木的旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有感受到什么\N不可思议的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛自己变的更诚实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得自己的心思\N也愈来愈清晰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当年接受你爸爸求婚的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈当然很喜欢你爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:16:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是求婚前几天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却为了一点琐事吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于能不能顺利的往下发展
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一走到这棵树下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己也变的更加诚实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是就OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏如此  得到了戈薇与草太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈很感谢这棵树
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈不会过问戈薇在烦恼什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是妈妈相信戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为戈薇是会朝自己\N深信的道路勇往直前的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都还没说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我去见戈薇对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然知道为什么不去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是那就等于向戈薇道别了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候没能说出口的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要传达给她才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在最痛苦的人不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是戈薇姑娘才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉是已经下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想戈薇现在一定非常苦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是男人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去找戈薇把话说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮的做个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  什么事都拖拖拉拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…巴不得我和戈薇分开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想分开吗\N你不想分开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨…谁会在意这种小事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经决定要保护桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的我怎能再说出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到戈薇身边这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不到黄河心不死的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后就叫他劈腿男吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还比他振作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能说“回来吧”这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇应该很清楚才对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有好好的见个面道别的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心里也放不下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在对面的这期间  我一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  桔梗还有我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为了解犬夜叉的心情  所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我已经不能再待在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:18:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在遇到你之前  谁都不信任我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  你会为了我而掉泪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是待在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和戈薇在一起我很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我无法时而高兴时而欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗追随着我而死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我必须舍命报答桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我比不上桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也考虑了许多桔梗的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗与我是完全不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使说我是桔梗的转世
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我毕竟不是桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心是我自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过\N我只能理解一种桔梗的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能再见犬夜叉一面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到桔梗\N也和我有相同的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就觉得轻松点了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然想要相见的心情是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才鼓起勇气来见犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也很想见你一面  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和犬夜叉在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我无法忘记你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇…我该怎么回答才好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问你一件事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和你在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要…和我在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.97,0:21:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉与桔梗的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不可能斩断的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点我清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是犬夜叉  我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.15,0:21:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你相遇绝对不是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.65,0:21:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望犬夜叉能继续活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.99,0:21:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.33,0:21:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你充满欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道能为你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想一直待在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:30.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,除了真正珍贵的东西{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:42.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,若能全都舍弃 那该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.28,0:22:49.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,只是现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:53.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:22:58.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.10,0:23:05.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,便能看见 你的笑容{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:12.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah- 但愿从此以往
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.15,0:23:19.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,直到进入 沉眠的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:27.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你的 那抹笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:35.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,都绝没有 消逝的瞬间{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.79,0:23:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投靠亲切的老爷爷\N与老婆婆的琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.76,0:23:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪竟然追来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.99,0:23:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是夺取背上的四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.80,0:23:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶然遇上的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:23:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将琥珀藏了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.03,0:24:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是琥珀完全想不起来
